net.algem.planning
Class Action

java.lang.Object
  net.algem.planning.Action
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, GemModel
public class Action
extends java.lang.Object
implements GemModel

An action ensures the grouping of several schedule objects. Each schedule of the group has the same action id. It facilitates the modification and the suppression of schedules and the recording of members on planning. An action is composed also of specific parameters (status, level, age range, etc.).

Since:
1.0a 07/07/1999
